{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九回\"仙境与地狱\"：楚留香猜出追杀他的人是水母阴姬（神水宫主人），因其失约未在限期内归还天一神水。众人讨论水母阴姬平生最恨男人、武功深不可测的传闻。楚留香决定主动前往神水宫解决问题。苏蓉蓉回忆她曾由姑姑指引，经桃花溪进入神水宫，所见如桃花源般仙境；柳无眉则讲述她通过菩提庵老尼姑进入后，遭遇阴湿地牢和各种恐怖气味的精神折磨，最终水母阴姬提出以楚留香人头换取解药。两种截然不同的神水宫经历形成鲜明对比，暗示神水宫表面美丽而内部凶险的双重本质。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不说我现在也已猜出那人是谁了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水母阴姬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这'水母阴姬'的名字我好像听过，却想不起是谁了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "水母阴姬就是神水娘娘，也就是神水宫的主人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我没有猜错吧?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然很少入关，但也听说这'水母阴姬'乃是武林中第一个怪人，据说她的脾气还有几分和石观音相似，平生最恨男人，无论任何男人，只要瞧了她一眼，她就绝不会让他再活下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "你弄错了，她的脾气和石观音一点也不相似，石观音非但不恨男人，而且还很喜欢男人，尤其是漂亮的男人，她的毛病只不过是对男人的胃口太大了而已，所以总是想换个新鲜的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但'水母阴姬'却是真的恨男人，据我所知，普天之下绝没有一个男人和她接近过，神水宫中更看不到一个男人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我也知道这人虽然喜怒无常，虽然很恨男人，但她却不是个坏人，也不像石观音那么样，想去害别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，只要别人不去惹她，她也绝不惹别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么，她为什么要杀你呢?你难道惹了她么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "我正是惹了她了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你们究竟有什么仇恨?我也不知道，因为我不敢问她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三四个月以前，神水宫中忽然失窃，丢了一瓶'天一神水'，神水宫的人竟怀疑是我偷的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "究竟是不是你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "自然不是我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也相信绝不是他，若是'天一神酒'，他也许还会偷来喝喝，'天一神水'他偷来又有什么用?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是'天一神醋'，我就知道是谁偷的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "小鬼，你才是个醋瓶子哩!",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天一神水我虽连见都没有见过，但神宫的人却不肯放过我，竟逼着要我在一个月中将偷水的那人找出来，否则她们就要来找我算账。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你找出了那人是谁么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我找出来了，只可惜那一阵子发生的事太多，我竟忘了神水宫给我的限期，也没有去向她们交代。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个有教养的男人，怎么能忘记他和女人的约会呢?这就难怪别人要来找你的麻烦了，我倒不怪她们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他根本就不该和她们约定的，那时他根本连一点把握也没有，这件事也根本和他无关，但他一瞧见那位眼波比海水还温柔的女孩子，他头就晕了，就糊里糊涂的答应了人家，现在神水宫……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神水宫也没有什么了不起，她们若来了，我们这里反正有'神醋宫'的掌门人对付她。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我夫妻蒙香帅开恩不杀，已是感激不尽，实在不能，也不敢再求香帅出手相救了，此后但望……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你不必认为我是要冒险去救你，反正我是非到神水宫去走一趟不可的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那种地方，香帅你不去也罢。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我怎么能不去，我若不去，以后的麻烦只怕更大了，那位'水母阴姬'既然能要你来杀我，也能要别人来杀我，我难道还能提防她一辈子么?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，他既然已失了约，就该去和人家讲个明白，我想那'水母阴姬'总不会是个蛮不讲理的人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你以为她是个很讲理的人么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她若真的不讲理，我们也有不讲理的法子对付她，那神水宫就是刀山火海，龙潭虎穴，我胡某人也要去闯一闯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神水宫既没有刀山火海，也不是龙潭虎穴，反而是个风景非常优美，有如仙境的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "对了，只有你是到神水宫去过的，你觉那地方是不是真的很可怕?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在我说来，那地方实在一点也不可怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可听到过传说中的桃花源么?神水宫就和桃花源一样，简直可说是人间的仙境，我到了那里之后，还无法相信那就是名震天下的神水宫，因那里非但没有杀气，连一点烟火气都没有。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时候正是初夏，我坐着条小船，沿溪而上，走了很久之后，就发觉有一瓣瓣桃花沿着溪水流下。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "是不是还有胡麻饭?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "花瓣中的确还有很香的胡麻饭，微风中花香更醉人，我坐在船上，非但好像已走入了图画，简直好像已走入了神话。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我如痴如醉，也不知船行了多久，渐渐走入一条山隙里，两旁都生着很浓密的水草，暗得伸手不见五指。我用桨拨着水草，又走了很久，眼前豁然开朗，只见眼前百花如锦，是一片锦绣山谷，右面一道瀑布自山巅飞挂而下，鸣珠贱玉，沁人心肺，花丛间隐隐可以见到一些亭台茅舍，还有几千几万只不知名的鸟在飞来飞去，见了人也不害怕，竟有几只飞到我的肩头，像是要和我说话。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "早知神水宫是这么样的仙境，我也该陪你去的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "但姑娘你又怎会知道这条小溪就是入山的途径呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我有个姑姑，是神水宫的门下，她曾经告诉过我，要去找她的时候应该怎么样去，她自然不准我将这秘密说给别人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "你姑姑也住在花丛间那些屋子里么?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "后来我才知道，花树丛中那些亭台茅舍，就是神水宫门下的居处，因为每个人的喜爱不同，是以她们住的屋子式样也不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "你姑姑住的地方是什么样子呢?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "她住的是两间很精致的茅舍，外面有竹篱，院子里还种着菊花，那时菊花虽然还没有开放，但我一到了那里，就不禁想起陶渊明的两句诗。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "采菊东篱下，悠然见南山……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这'水母阴姬'对她的徒弟，实在比石观音要好得多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我到了那里之后，并不能四下游逛，只能待在我姑姑的屋子里，因为她警告过我，我若到处乱跑，立刻就会有很大的灾祸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "什么灾祸?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她也没有说出是什么灾祸，只是将我关在屋子里，不让我见人，所以我连那位宫南燕姑娘都没有见到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "如此说来，你也没有见到'水母阴姬'了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "你也不知道她住在什么地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在很想见见这位武林中的传奇人物，但我姑姑却再三警告我，不让我见她，可是我知道她的确也住在那片山谷里，也许就在我姑姑茅舍对面那片桃花林中，也许就在山坡前那小小的尼庵里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "尼庵?神水宫中难道也有尼姑么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "据说'水母阴姬'是位很虔诚的居士，所以她才会让'妙僧'无花入谷去解说佛经。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，她的确很可能就住在那尼庵里的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但据我所知，无花也并没有见过她，无花入谷后，每天都要坐在瀑布前的大石上讲两个时辰佛经，他也知道'水母阴姬'每天都在听他讲经，却始终没有见到她的人究竟在哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她实在是个很神秘的人物，比我想像中还要神秘得多。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这神水宫却没有我想像中神秘，我本来以为那地方一定很阴森可怕，谁知却比世上大多数地方都可爱得多。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位莫要忘了，我也到神水宫去过的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你自然去过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据我所知，神水宫并不是苏姑娘所说的那种地方。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "哦?你见到的神水宫难道有什么不同么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有很大的不同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苏姑娘见到的神水宫，是人间仙境，我见到的神水宫，却是人间地狱。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有姑姑指点我入山的途径，所以费了许多功夫，才打听出想到神水宫去的人，一定要先经过菩提庵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "这菩提庵既和神水宫关系如此密切，自然也必定是个很有名的地方，我怎地从未听过这名字?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这菩提庵只不过是间很破烂的小庙，庵里也只有一个尼姑，这尼姑看来至少已经有七八十岁了，而且似乎又聋又哑，但无论什么人，要想到神水宫去，就得将自己为什么要去的原因，告诉这老尼姑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "这老尼姑既然又聋又哑，怎么能听到别人说话?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她若不肯让你到神水宫去，她就又聋又哑，你无论怎么求她，她都听不见，但她若肯让你去，你说的每一个字，她都听得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这法子倒真不错。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我对她说出我想到神水宫去的理由之后，她沉默了很久，忽然倒了杯茶，要我喝下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你喝下去了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我怎么能不喝呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自然也知道这杯茶不是好喝的，喝下去之后，我果然立刻昏迷了过去，等我醒来的时候，我发现竟已被关在一只箱子里，箱子水淋淋的，像是在水里泡过，我身上也全都湿透了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神水宫必定有处水源，至少这一点是没有疑问的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "神水中没有水，难道还有酒吗?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么也瞧不见，只有摸着往前走，既不知道这条地道究竟有多长，也不知道这地道是通向哪里的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你至少可以确定，这条地道里绝不会有人来暗算你，因为'水母阴姬'至少不会是个暗算别人的人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我眼睛和耳朵虽然都没有用了，但鼻子却还有用，因为那地道中竟有各式各样不同的气味。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "什……什么气味?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "起先是一阵阵潮湿的气味，接着又有一阵阵火烧的气味，像是有东西被烧焦了，后来又有血腥气、铁屑气、泥土气、木头气……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在那地道中，虽然没有任何人来暗算过我，也没有任何陷阱，但就只这么不同的气味，已逼得我快发疯了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "这些气味又不能伤人，有什么可怕的呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我本来也想不到气味会有什么可怕的，但到了那时，我才知道世上没有任何事比这气味更可怕的了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我闻到火烧气的时候，开始还不觉得怎样，后来只觉得我仿佛是走在一个很大的火炉里，在被人焚烧着。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我闻到血腥气和铁屑气的时候，只觉四面都是死尸，好像有成千上万个死尸，躲在黑暗中，我连路都不敢走了，只因我觉得再走一步，说不定就会踩在一具死尸上，而且说不定就是我朋友的死尸。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等我闻到泥土气和木头气的时候，我自己像是也已变成了一具死尸，已被放在棺材里，埋在地下。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来以为一个人只会为了眼睛见到的事而害怕，为了耳朵听到的声音而害怕，到了那时，我才知道鼻子嗅到的气味，才是最令人害怕的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只怕是因为眼睛所见的，和耳朵所听的都比较实在些，而鼻子所嗅到的，却虚无缥缈，不可捉摸，你只有用幻想去猜测，越想就越可怕。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以在那地道中，我虽然什么也没有瞧见，什么也没有听见，就已被折磨得连一丝力气都没有，连走都走不动了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "后……后来呢?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在那时，地道中忽然响起了一个人的声音，那声音听来虽然很柔美，但我那时却只觉她阴凄凄的，竟不像是人的声音。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "她……她……她说什么?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她说，她已看过我的病势，也知道我中的是什么毒了，但我若想她出手来救我，就要……就要……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "就要将我的头拿去给她，是不是?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我虽然再三哀求她，问她还有没有别的路可走，但她却再也不理我了，我说得声音都已嘶哑，她却像是根本一个字都没有听到。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    }
  ],
